title: Black Eyed Peas Interview and More

description:
Wednesay 1/17 - Today on the show we had the group Black Eyed Peas in the building where they spoke about their new single "Street Livin" and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to PnB Rock after he peed on his hotel floor because he was getting kicked out the hotel for smoking; which he was not suppose to be doing in the first place. Also Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
